Program: Outlook
Title: Kept as a Slave
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrxz
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
***Warning: some listeners may find this audio upsetting*** Olivia was brought from Togo to France after her mother died. She was kept as a slave and experienced horrific violence. Her account contains descriptions of the torture she endured. Also on the programme a foster mother who has cared for 18 children; a woman who is considering a whole body list and a man who wants to swap a paper clip for a house. Presented by Heather Payton. Show less